{"tid":709674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳浮潛捕魚客日增 「滅絕式捕魚」　海洋生態堪憂　政府應加強監管","createTime":"2018-06-20T08:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T09:09:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dd841179abe4eacdc47daeaad0da723153b2bf15","tid":709674,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:15:11.000Z","msg":"近日，Facebook專頁「山野龍咁威」發布網民的漁獲照片，其漁獲之豐，被網民批評為「滅絕式捕魚」。其實網絡間早充斥捕魚群組，當中不少更涉及經濟活動，涉嫌違法，相關部門必須正視問題，研究「休閒捕魚」對本地生態造成的影響，考慮訂立相應措施，保育自然生態。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1557378/org/7babea798f945bdc2a42ffc8e5aa2f78.jpg/bhEq1zxL2VD74ESZYcpXNbQjhPHl7oB_PgniOT4J4jk?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1557378%2Forg%2F7babea798f945bdc2a42ffc8e5aa2f78.jpg%2FbhEq1zxL2VD74ESZYcpXNbQjhPHl7oB_PgniOT4J4jk%3Fv%3Dw480&h=1486a1c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1557363/org/9de323eac7eb9eb546d9e1217eddf053.jpg/okzjDeuDh37EIkBZyLIiYlMbcyh4rvHxxNsiccTbInE?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1557363%2Forg%2F9de323eac7eb9eb546d9e1217eddf053.jpg%2FokzjDeuDh37EIkBZyLIiYlMbcyh4rvHxxNsiccTbInE%3Fv%3Dw800&h=c1e38cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1557381/org/078fc387a510885f60b1869f178c373a.jpg/T-tnV5_7SbvRrn6HirGr_dd-nHAPsfkfrBBssKwQbLA?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1557381%2Forg%2F078fc387a510885f60b1869f178c373a.jpg%2FT-tnV5_7SbvRrn6HirGr_dd-nHAPsfkfrBBssKwQbLA%3Fv%3Dw480&h=df4a170e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1557376/org/5e60f0c196dd9e3ca46585c1a7cec1ee.jpg/TRP_3MX24MDAC7mvd-6TDq0gYtuSAhWG2OTLW9jky1s?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1557376%2Forg%2F5e60f0c196dd9e3ca46585c1a7cec1ee.jpg%2FTRP_3MX24MDAC7mvd-6TDq0gYtuSAhWG2OTLW9jky1s%3Fv%3Dw480&h=7bde87c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1557380/org/fdb290328c648e9e37e0f3e308dce73d.jpg/ln-GhiKr6Yj5bjUXDzTNqKw7XS7b8i9kAnUHigJ1B4o?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1557380%2Forg%2Ffdb290328c648e9e37e0f3e308dce73d.jpg%2Fln-GhiKr6Yj5bjUXDzTNqKw7XS7b8i9kAnUHigJ1B4o%3Fv%3Dw480&h=f3c9ba47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1557375/org/2088c6992c2cabbf4d4cdda877d5333c.jpg/0ACXmWicds6FsxRHt-Buo1wv2_82wh9qovQ896L0PPc?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1557375%2Forg%2F2088c6992c2cabbf4d4cdda877d5333c.jpg%2F0ACXmWicds6FsxRHt-Buo1wv2_82wh9qovQ896L0PPc%3Fv%3Dw800&h=5f481ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1557397/org/eedfe7ff6eca9ce790db918bb157ee68.jpg/xb1wuBqKRk1dDZXjKsQfaYzpHlCj0ANLKqR9giqkfYI?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1557397%2Forg%2Feedfe7ff6eca9ce790db918bb157ee68.jpg%2Fxb1wuBqKRk1dDZXjKsQfaYzpHlCj0ANLKqR9giqkfYI%3Fv%3Dw800&h=ff0f33ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1557404/org/c0452df1b103ee3e669d13978a930f28.jpg/ovfZDXtqaRfZ-zvqP7l5pmONuuOJ4eEt3qcyw96nMsM?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1557404%2Forg%2Fc0452df1b103ee3e669d13978a930f28.jpg%2FovfZDXtqaRfZ-zvqP7l5pmONuuOJ4eEt3qcyw96nMsM%3Fv%3Dw480&h=dd51d03a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n群組內部分魚獲用作出售。/不少網民展示本地魚刺身（網絡圖片）<br />\n<br />\n自2012年《漁業保護條例》訂修開始，政府已然禁止拖網捕魚，並要求本地漁船登記，限制本地商業漁船的數量，漁農自然護理署署長有權規管登記漁船的引擎功率、可捕魚的範圍、捕魚方法及使用的捕魚用具等等。當時條例只針對商業捕魚，未有加強消閒捕魚的規管，原因也許是政府認為其影響力有限，不足為憂。<br />\n<br />\n現行法例對於消閒釣魚活動的規管不多。就水塘而言，水務署轄下的十七個水塘及九個灌溉用水塘於魚類非繁殖季節（即每年九月一日至翌年三月三十一日）開放予市民釣魚，惟市民須事先到水務署申請牌照，並繳交牌費。海釣方面，市民在非海岸公園範圍內釣魚一般不受規管。在捕魚器具方面，如果市民未有使用毒物、電擊、魚炮等方式捕魚，也不涉違法。<br />\n<br />\n誠然，垂釣本屬健康活動，政府不應過度規管，窒礙發展，但是一些害群之馬濫捕、乃至出售魚獲的舉動，卻絕不可取。觀乎網絡圖片，市民的魚獲已然和職業魚民相差無幾，政府在釐清法例灰色地帶、加強執法之餘，還需研究消閒捕魚對生態的潛在影響，訂立應對措施。<br />\n<br />\n《海魚（統營和輸出）規例》就魚類買賣作出嚴格規管，如無許可證，漁船只能於漁市場將海魚卸在陸上。固然，《規例》豁免「運動或消遣中被捕獲（的魚類）」，但是群組中的市民將魚類出售，照理已不符合運動、消遣的定義，其經網上平台出售海魚，有違法之嫌。如果網上出售海鮮屬於違法，相關部門必須嚴厲執法，禁絕相關行為。<br />\n<br />\n魚統處分別在香港仔、筲箕灣、觀塘、長沙灣、青山、大埔及西貢經營7個魚類批發市場，為漁民、魚類批發商及買家提供有效率及有秩序之批銷服務。（資料來源：魚類統營處）<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，政府亦需正視消閒捕魚活動所造成的影響，研究擴充發牌制度至海釣的可能性。早於2010年，立法會議員黃容根就曾於「促進釣魚活動發展」議案建議成立釣魚牌照制度，當時食物及衞生局局長周一嶽在議案總結發言回應指，「本地康樂釣魚活動對漁業資源所構成的壓力不大」，未有接納相關建議。然而，隨着網上平台大行其道，民間捕魚人數有上升之勢，政府必須重新審運動釣魚造成的影響。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，不少歐美地區已就消閒釣魚作出規管，以加拿大安大略省為例，當地規定除原居民外，市民釣魚前必須領有牌照，條例也限制釣魚客的捕魚方式、數量，以保育自然生態。固然香港在這階段就休閒釣魚訂立發牌機制，似乎言之尚早，但是如果問題日趨嚴重，政府就必須考慮實施監管，杜絕害群之馬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/200911/%E6%B5%AE%E6%BD%9B%E6%8D%95%E9%AD%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%A5%E5%A2%9E-%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B%E7%94%9F%E6%85%8B%E5%A0%AA%E6%86%82-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%87%89%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E8%25A7%2580%25E9%25BB%259E%2F200911%2F%25E6%25B5%25AE%25E6%25BD%259B%25E6%258D%2595%25E9%25AD%259A%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A2%259E-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25B4%258B%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2585%258B%25E5%25A0%25AA%25E6%2586%2582-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%25AE%25A1&d=hxHaN75OGENS4KVQpwmOQAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=8ab6ab55\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/200911/%E6%B5%AE%E6%BD%9B%E6%8D%95%E9%AD%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%A5%E5%A2%9E-%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B%E7%94%9F%E6%85%8B%E5%A0%AA%E6%86%82-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%87%89%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1</a>"},{"pid":"3cf3ac33e8090b06df4e43c694a143f6384c10dc","tid":709674,"uid":30085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"刺身 wtf <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe00162203350aebf2c7075263c5b8901bec22eb","tid":709674,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3cf3ac33e8090b06df4e43c694a143f6384c10dc","tid":709674,"uid":30085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"刺身 wtf <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:18:50.000Z","msg":"班友都short既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d782130fadc660c9417a74183e03974ed329cfd3","tid":709674,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"食撚死佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db5c6160da1338766fe9bff22fc23fe2dc9b966","tid":709674,"uid":2214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以分翻清楚 fb賣魚果班係潛水打魚果班<br />\n依家乜都係話釣魚"},{"pid":"e08011fe79073f1fd98126e2ed4d26c56e5df736","tid":709674,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浮潛捉魚跟本冇錯<br />\n<br />\n釣魚、漁業對海洋生態破壞仲大<br />\n1）冇得選擇性捉，一定捉、釣埋好多唔食得嘅水底生物（海龜、鯊魚、魚苗）<br />\n2）唔會有魚網遺留海底問題<br />\n3）一啖氣、體力有限，但漁船拖網、釣魚唔洗體力、反壓技巧，門檻低過潛水捉魚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論，傳媒鳩up誇大，要禁就禁哂全港釣魚、釣墨魚、拖網捕魚先"},{"pid":"05b41d587833809a2c5ddd0b45644c83a4086bf3","tid":709674,"uid":82929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/163435_ce33248f55f7f8b23091f3ee7d5907c1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F163435_ce33248f55f7f8b23091f3ee7d5907c1.png&h=342cfdf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"p